- recording_id: 1
  steps:
  - description: Rinse a tomato
  - description: gently dry it with a tea towel
  - description: "Slice one tomato into about \xBD inch thick slices"
  - description: Place the thick slices of tomatoes on a platter, ensuring they only
      make a single layer
  - description: Season the tomato slices with salt
  - description: Sprinkle mozzarella cheese on top of the tomato throughout the platter
  - description: "Season with \xBC teaspoon black pepper"
  - description: Garnish with seasoning
  - description: Add a drizzle of extra-virgin olive oil, about 1 tablespoon, over
      the entire platter
